                     <interp inst="t18381022-2297-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18381022-2297-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>for stealing, on the <rs id="t18381022-cd-43" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18381022-2297-offence-1 t18381022-cd-43"></join>16th of Octo<lb></lb>ber</rs>, 1 handkerchief, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of—<persName id="t18381022-name-280" type="victimName">
